instructions: Open your phone's Settings app. Tap Tips & support . Tap Email or Chat . Type your information. Tap Send . We ll email or chat with you!
Open your phone s Settings app. Tap the setting. Tap Help . If you don't see "Help," you're running a different Android version. Tap More .

Open your phone s Settings app. Tap Tips & support . Pick how you'd like to find your information. To read a suggested article, tap it. To search for a topic, tap where it says "Describe your issue." To see what topics there are, tap Browse all articles .
